description:
Today we take our first look into the Minecraft 1.7 Update! Snapshot 13w36a was released a few hours ago and i took my time going through all the new items, blocks, features etc etc... and of course the biomes! When there are lots of updates there are always things you miss so i thought id list them here :-)

Missed Changes:
Confirm quit menu
Packed ice doesn't melt
Giants spawned with commands
